MLK Community Healthcare Sponsored It’s easy to interview for a nursing position at MLK Community Healthcare. Walk in any weekday between 9 a.m. – 3 p.m. You'll meet our nurse recruiter, learn about our competitive benefits and career advancement programs, and enjoy a delicious lunch on us!

MLK Community Healthcare Sponsored Tuition reimbursement. Loan forgiveness eligibility. 403(b). Free Medical, dental, and vision. Self-scheduling. Nurse Wellbeing Programs. And more! At MLK Community Healthcare, we offer our nurses all of these great benefits. Add an inspirational mission and our warm, supportive culture and you have an unbeatable recipe for nursing success.

MLK Community Healthcare Sponsored Massage chairs, meditation – and more! At MLK Community Healthcare, we invest in the health and wellbeing of our nurses through programs that nourish the mind, body and spirit. Our unique Nurse Wellbeing Program offers guided meditation and yoga, relaxation rooms, pet therapy and more. Healthy nurses are happy nurses so join us and wake up each day with a smile!
